uted to the anti-Semitism exhibited by adherents of radical forms of Islam in the Middle East today.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAntisemitismxHistoryx20th centuryxArab countries. 0aAntisemitismzArab countriesxHistoryy20th century. 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945). 0aNazi propagandaxHistoryx20th centuryxArab countries. 0aNazi propagandazArab countriesxHistoryy20th century. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xPropaganda. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015583940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300155839423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300155839/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles